{
    "title": "Authorize.Net Unsettled Transactions",
    "description": "This dashboard provides a comprehensive view of unsettled transactions in Authorize.Net, highlighting Total Unsettled Transactions and the Average Amount per Transaction. It categorizes transactions by Account Type, Market Type, Product, Status, and Customer Profile ID, while also tracking Held Transactions and trends over time. Financial metrics, such as amounts grouped by various attributes, offer insights into the overall impact of unsettled transactions, helping to identify potential issues and ensure timely resolution.",
